node.title: Five Omicron cases linked to indoor gym, Western Sydney schools
node.alt: A building with the sign indoor climbing
node.description: There are now five Omicron cases connected to a cluster at an indoor climbing gym and two Western Sydney schools, bringing to 15 the total number of confirmed cases of the  COVID-19 variant across the state.
node.content:
["NSW Health authorities say there are now five Omicron cases connected to a\u00a0cluster at an indoor climbing gym and two Western Sydney schools.", "A confirmed case in the ACT has also been linked to the\u00a0Sydney Indoor Climbing Gym at Villawood.", "There are now 15 cases\u00a0of COVID-19 with the Omicron variant across the state.", "The outbreak of cases connected to\u00a0Regents Park Christian School and the indoor gym has now spread to\u00a0a primary school in Regents Park.", "A student from\u00a0St Peter Chanel Catholic Primary School in Regents Park is confirmed as a new case of Omicron, after going to the indoor gym on November 27.", "All year three and year four students and teachers at the school have been deemed close contacts and asked to self-isolate.", "Genomic sequencing is underway on a number of other cases linked to the schools and gym, NSW Health said.", "Anyone who was at the Sydney Indoor Climbing Gym in Villawood\u00a0on Saturday, November 27, between 9am and 4.30pm is considered a close contact and must get tested and isolate for seven days.\u00a0", "So far, nobody with the Omicron variant has been admitted to hospital for treatment in NSW.", "New South Wales has recorded 286 new COVID-19 cases and 1 death in the past 24 hours to 8pm last night.", "A man aged in his 60s from south-eastern Sydney has\u00a0died at St George Hospital.", "NSW Health said he had received two doses of a COVID-19 vaccine and had underlying health conditions.", "There were 66,671 COVID-19 tests reported to 8pm last night, down from\u00a068,435 the previous day.", "Several cases confirmed as the Omicron variant travelled back to NSW on flights from overseas destinations in late November.", "Anyone who has\u00a0been\u00a0in South Africa, Lesotho, Botswana, Zimbabwe, Mozambique, Namibia, Eswatini and Malawi 14-days before arriving\u00a0in NSW must go into\u00a0hotel quarantine for 14 days, irrespective of their\u00a0vaccination.", "Those who have visited\u00a0any of the eight African countries within the previous 14 days must\u00a0get tested and isolate for 14 days, and call NSW Health.", "To date, 92.8 per cent of New South Wales residents\u00a0aged 16 and over have had two doses of a COVID-19 vaccine.", "", "
Why we hear about some COVID-19 variants more than others
"]
